  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074690/extras/bb89b61c31f84d279470a0baea3575c5.avif?t=1658128040\" width=480 height=270 /></span><br><br>You are Edda, a young girl lost in a dying world.<br>The elements of the world have been unleashed, ancient demons stalk the lands.<br>Collect the pieces of Quintessence, ascend to a divine power, defeat the elder god<br>harvesting the souls of the world.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2074690/extras/df049d698e20f7baff98aa751c63d284.avif?t=1658128040\" width=400 height=113 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Short but replayable story<br></li><li> High intensity combat, Dodge, Slash, and Shoot your way to victory!<br></li><li> Story Rich experience, explore the morality behind ambition and loneliness</li></ul>",
